{"tid":1655423,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[街坊] 以後應該叫番狗竇,唔係收隊,徹底摧毁佢地自尊","createTime":"2019-10-15T05:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T11:01:23.000Z","uid":254330,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"abfb44bf6569fad8c47e380cfeb48bf2f7d7386f","tid":1655423,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"首先多謝各位黎自唔同地區嘅<span style=\"color: gold;\">街坊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直幫手屌狗屌到佢地燥底,發火,係鏡頭前面發老脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係咁撚狗,撚到佢地出醜,柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地仲要經常係空裝嘅情況下食左唔少tear gas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Thanks for your support!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入正題,其實樓豬未試過做街坊,戴番頭盔先,所以可能講嘅野你地已經做緊!<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">番狗竇</span></span><br />\n1. 叫<span style=\"color: red;\">番狗竇</span>,而唔係收隊。我通常第日睇番apple daily都會見到街坊不斷咁叫收隊收隊收隊,有冇諗過試下改叫<span style=\"color: red;\">番狗竇</span>?狗唔係一個隊伍唔係一個team,佢地番嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">狗竇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,比<span style=\"color: red;\">狗</span>住嘅,咁樣可以進一步令佢地失去自尊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">過街老鼠</span></span><br />\n2. 唔單止要叫佢地做黑社會,要叫佢地做<span style=\"color: red;\">過街老鼠</span>!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎狗</span></span><br />\n3. 唔知班狗比街坊叫<span style=\"color: red;\">食屎狗</span>會有咩感受呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上都係堆言語,用字上嘅建議,務求令各位街坊撚狗撚得更開心,更happy,同時令班狗同green object更易發火失控,完全control唔到自己嘅emotion<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,發曬脾氣,係一片謾罵聲之下<span style=\"color: red;\">番狗竇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,為佢地造成更大嘅心理壓力同更傷佢地自尊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>  順祝  <br />\n各位街坊<br />\n屌狗順利,撚狗開心,玩狗精神,越玩越過癮!越撚越興奮!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c911d24a5aece0fceedcc86fbd91b8b0f28adf7","tid":1655423,"uid":54262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"仲有散仔"},{"pid":"079cc077f583c652aa594a0f392a7ff6b32bd84d","tid":1655423,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 番狗竇番狗竇番狗竇番狗竇番狗竇番狗竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b98f9b5e6e53a9fda3d1a6bd76770ac611e2e0","tid":1655423,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:09:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">番狗竇番狗竇</span></span>"},{"pid":"f2ec0122b01b6b622927efa426e1bd859c36cef9","tid":1655423,"uid":311591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply